  "translations": {
    "en": "O! Hisham indeed Allah Blessed be and Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl and nsr alnbyyn balbyan and guided them upon rbwbyth baladlh so he said and your God a god one not god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. indeed in khlq the heavens and the earth and alternation the night and alnhar and alflk which (f) flow in the sea bma benefits the people and what sent down Allah from the sky from ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha and bth fyha from every dabh and tsryf the winds and the clouds almskhr between the sky and the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "ur": "اے Hisham بے شک Allah Blessed be اور Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl اور nsr alnbyyn balbyan اور guided them پر rbwbyth baladlh so he said اور your God a god one نہیں god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. بے شک میں khlq the heavens اور the earth اور alternation the night اور alnhar اور alflk which (f) flow میں the sea bma benefits the people اور what sent down Allah سے the sky سے ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha اور bth fyha سے every dabh اور tsryf the winds اور the clouds almskhr between the sky اور the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "tr": "ey Hisham muhakkak Allah Blessed be ve Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl ve nsr alnbyyn balbyan ve guided them üzerine rbwbyth baladlh so he said ve your God a god one değil god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. muhakkak içinde khlq the heavens ve the earth ve alternation the night ve alnhar ve alflk which (f) flow içinde the sea bma benefits the people ve what sent down Allah -den the sky -den ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha ve bth fyha -den every dabh ve tsryf the winds ve the clouds almskhr between the sky ve the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "fa": "ای Hisham به درستی Allah Blessed be و Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl و nsr alnbyyn balbyan و guided them بر rbwbyth baladlh so he said و your God a god one نه god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. به درستی در khlq the heavens و the earth و alternation the night و alnhar و alflk which (f) flow در the sea bma benefits the people و what sent down Allah از the sky از ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha و bth fyha از every dabh و tsryf the winds و the clouds almskhr between the sky و the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "id": "wahai Hisham sesungguhnya Allah Blessed be dan Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl dan nsr alnbyyn balbyan dan guided them atas rbwbyth baladlh so he said dan your God a god one tidak god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. sesungguhnya di dalam khlq the heavens dan the earth dan alternation the night dan alnhar dan alflk which (f) flow di dalam the sea bma benefits the people dan what sent down Allah dari the sky dari ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha dan bth fyha dari every dabh dan tsryf the winds dan the clouds almskhr between the sky dan the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "bn": "হে Hisham নিশ্চয়ই Allah Blessed be এবং Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl এবং nsr alnbyyn balbyan এবং guided them উপর rbwbyth baladlh so he said এবং your God a god one না god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. নিশ্চয়ই মধ্যে khlq the heavens এবং the earth এবং alternation the night এবং alnhar এবং alflk which (f) flow মধ্যে the sea bma benefits the people এবং what sent down Allah থেকে the sky থেকে ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha এবং bth fyha থেকে every dabh এবং tsryf the winds এবং the clouds almskhr between the sky এবং the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "es": "oh Hisham ciertamente Allah Blessed be y Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl y nsr alnbyyn balbyan y guided them sobre rbwbyth baladlh so he said y your God a god one no god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. ciertamente en khlq the heavens y the earth y alternation the night y alnhar y alflk which (f) flow en the sea bma benefits the people y what sent down Allah de the sky de ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha y bth fyha de every dabh y tsryf the winds y the clouds almskhr between the sky y the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "fr": "ô Hisham certes Allah Blessed be et Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl et nsr alnbyyn balbyan et guided them sur rbwbyth baladlh so he said et your God a god one non god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. certes dans khlq the heavens et the earth et alternation the night et alnhar et alflk which (f) flow dans the sea bma benefits the people et what sent down Allah de the sky de ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha et bth fyha de every dabh et tsryf the winds et the clouds almskhr between the sky et the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "de": "o Hisham wahrlich Allah Blessed be und Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl und nsr alnbyyn balbyan und guided them auf rbwbyth baladlh so he said und your God a god one nicht god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. wahrlich in khlq the heavens und the earth und alternation the night und alnhar und alflk which (f) flow in the sea bma benefits the people und what sent down Allah von the sky von ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha und bth fyha von every dabh und tsryf the winds und the clouds almskhr between the sky und the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "ru": "о Hisham поистине Allah Blessed be и Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl и nsr alnbyyn balbyan и guided them на rbwbyth baladlh so he said и your God a god one не god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. поистине в khlq the heavens и the earth и alternation the night и alnhar и alflk which (f) flow в the sea bma benefits the people и what sent down Allah из the sky из ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha и bth fyha из every dabh и tsryf the winds и the clouds almskhr between the sky и the earth layat for a people they reason",
    "zh": "啊 Hisham 确实 Allah Blessed be 和 Most High most complete llnas alhjj bal'qwl 和 nsr alnbyyn balbyan 和 guided them 在...上 rbwbyth baladlh so he said 和 your God a god one 不 god except he/it the Most Merciful the Most Merciful. 确实 在 khlq the heavens 和 the earth 和 alternation the night 和 alnhar 和 alflk which (f) flow 在 the sea bma benefits the people 和 what sent down Allah 从 the sky 从 ma' fahya by it the earth after mwtha 和 bth fyha 从 every dabh 和 tsryf the winds 和 the clouds almskhr between the sky 和 the earth layat for a people they reason"
